🌐 Product Showcase Website
A responsive web app built with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PHP, and MySQL. Users can browse a catalog, register an account, sign in, and manage a shopping basket. This was created for a university web development module.

🎯 Features
Product listing homepage

User login and sign-up system

Shopping basket with session support

About and contact pages

PHP–MySQL database integration

🛠 Tech Stack
HTML, CSS, JavaScript

PHP (server-side)

MySQL (database)

XAMPP / phpMyAdmin for local development


📁 File Structure
index.php – main homepage

log.php / sign.php – user auth pages

product.php / basket.php – product views and cart

Database.php – connects to the MySQL database

/img – images

/css – styling

